item.title: Some Questions
item.dc:creator: @k0j0e k0j0e
item.description:
@k0j0e wrote:

  1. To change npc health open npc.cfg and find your monster name…you gonna see that

npc = 1 Man 2 7

the 2 is the lvl and the 7 is the hp…

YOU CANT CHANGE THE LVL… i think…

  1. To remove object, open client.java and search for Deleteobjects

        deletethatobject(3509, 9497);

the (3509, 9497); is the coords of the object…

so put the correct coords and compile… =P
